WEBVTT

00:10:29.373 --> 00:10:32.095
He has been diagnosed with a mental illness

00:10:32.095 --> 00:10:34.929
for which he has been properly medicated.

00:10:34.929 --> 00:10:38.297
I adopted Kevin when he was only six months old,

00:10:38.297 --> 00:10:42.245
completely unaware of any hereditary traits,

00:10:42.245 --> 00:10:46.429
but, thank God, now we know.

00:10:46.429 --> 00:10:49.255
Kevin is straight, as he says.

00:10:49.255 --> 00:10:51.940
We truly thank God for you.

00:10:51.940 --> 00:10:54.341
Sincerely indebted to you,

00:10:54.341 --> 00:10:57.033
Narvella Berthia."

00:10:57.033 --> 00:10:59.081
And on the bottom she writes,

00:10:59.081 --> 00:11:04.517
"P.S. When I visited San Francisco
General Hospital that evening,